{"name":"Phantoms","permission":{"default":0,"JgpLZkPryhl1EFab":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_xwkwe74aoze","path":"Pathfinder RPG - Occult Adventures Reference Library#/CF_SEP/Occult Adventures#/CF_SEP/CHAPTER 1: OCCULT CLASSES","color":"#000000"}},"content":"<text type=\"formattedtext\"></text><text type=\"formattedtext\"><p>A phantom's abilities are determined by the spiritualist's level and the choice of manifestations the spiritualist makes when she performs the manifestation ritual. Table 1-11: Manifested Phantom's Base Statistics on page 77 determines many of the base statistics of the phantom. Each phantom possesses an emotional focus that modifies these base statistics and abilities. Phantoms are considered outsiders for the purpose of determining which spells affect them.</p></text>\n            <text type=\"formattedtext\"><h1>Table 1-11: Manifested Phantom's Base Statistics</h1><table><tr decoration=\"underline\"><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Class Level</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>HD</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>BAB</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Good Saves</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Bad Save</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Skills</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Feats</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Armor Bonus</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Dex/Cha Bonus</b></td><td colspan=\"2\"><b>Slam Damage*</b></td><td colspan=\"5\"><b>Special</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\">1st</td><td colspan=\"2\">1</td><td colspan=\"2\">+1</td><td colspan=\"2\">+2</td><td colspan=\"2\">+0</td><td colspan=\"2\">2</td><td colspan=\"2\">1</td><td colspan=\"2\">+0</td><td colspan=\"2\">+0</td><td colspan=\"2\">1d6</td><td colspan=\"5\">Darkvision, link, share spells</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\">2nd</td><td colspan=\"2\">2</td><td colspan=\"2\">+2</td><td colspan=\"2\">+3</td><td colspan=\"2\">+0</td><td colspan=\"2\">4</td><td colspan=\"2\">1</td><td colspan=\"2\">+2</td><td colspan=\"2\">+1</td><td colspan=\"2\">1d6</td><td colspan=\"5\">-</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\">3rd</td><td colspan=\"2\"